<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - The Limelight</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Roboto:wght@300;400&display=swap');
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #333 0%, #555 100%);
            color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2em 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        header::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 80%);
            animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes rotate {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin-bottom: 0.2em;
            position: relative;
        }
        .tagline {
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 3em;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            margin-top: -50px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 3em;
            position: relative;
        }
        .section::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: -20px;
            top: 0;
            height: 100%;
            width: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #333, transparent);
        }
        .section h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            border-bottom: none;
            padding-bottom: 0.5em;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        }
        .section p, .section ul {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #444;
        }
        .section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }
        .section ul li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .section ul li::before {
            content: "â€¢";
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: -5px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .content {
                padding: 2em;
                margin-top: -30px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
            }
            .section::before {
                left: -10px;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .content {
                padding: 1.5em;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            .section h2 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>The Limelight</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Illuminating Minds, Inspiring Thoughts</p>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <section class="section">
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p>The Limelight aspires to be the premier web magazine in English, dedicated to showcasing original, incisive, and open-minded perspectives on philosophy, culture, arts, and religion. We aim to create a platform where innovative ideas can flourish and engage readers in meaningful discourse.</p>
            </section>
            <section class="section">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is twofold: to curate thought-provoking content that challenges conventional wisdom and to provide a stage for emerging talented writers. We strive to present a diverse array of literary works, including captivating stories, evocative poems, controversial articles, and engaging travelogues.</p>
            </section>
            <section class="section">
                <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Commitment to originality and innovation in thought</li>
                    <li>Platform for both established and emerging voices</li>
                    <li>Interdisciplinary approach to culture and ideas</li>
                    <li>Fostering open dialogue and intellectual curiosity</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            <section class="section">
                <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
                <p>Whether you're a reader seeking to expand your horizons or a writer looking to share your unique perspective, The Limelight welcomes you. Together, let's explore the depths of human creativity and intellect, shining a light on ideas that truly matter.</p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>